{"tid":466054,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做開3D rendering?","createTime":"2017-11-12T07:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T06:32:07.000Z","uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"91fa140579a4a5bc4a602ff24432ec9b112cd6e5","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"香港好似好小公司做呢行，上網搵工都搵唔到<br />\n3D黎講，香港主流好似係unity 3D同埋auto-cad,因為香港市場比較多architecture，極其量都係用3d studio max<br />\n但外國主流3D軟件係maya,cinema 4d,3ds max,zbrush,blender等等<br />\n而且rendering會用外置既renderer,好似hollywood電影會用arnold renderer,有D廣告公司就會用octane renderer,仲有其他renderer如VRAY,maxwell...<br />\n我一直都係外面做緊呢行，唔知香港呢一行係點，屋企人有事，可能遲D要返香流照顧佢地，我剩係識做3D，好驚返香港會搵唔到工。。。<br />\n有冇巴打做緊呢行可以分享下？"},{"pid":"fcb29fdf90bd6ff0d0d60104880204ff0620ee23","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5862d31cbd3f85e99226792e8fa121317abe9b0d","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305964741b41a9a39bce7568ad689bbbdd278133","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca49c5771c466b759311d80448c80db48edfce25","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5808062354ef18524e4825748657e3657e7233","tid":466054,"uid":107345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港好似好小公司做呢行，上網搵工都搵唔到<br />\n3D黎講，香港主流好似係unity 3D同埋auto-cad,因為香港市場比較多architecture，極其量都係用3d studio max<br />\n但外國主流3D軟件係maya,cinema 4d,3ds max,zbrush,blender等等<br 