\nwho is BBA 畢業生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd54da459d5273edd5ecae5274ce947c7c79036","tid":466054,"uid":31530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"少囉<br />\n你畫邊類Render多<br />\n老實講好多公司將Render比大陸喱做<br />\n因為平兼快"},{"pid":"7add5f9ca028844d5d6e13573dc77b67cb194ad3","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少囉<br />\n你畫邊類Render多<br />\n老實講好多公司將Render比大陸喱做<br />\n因為平兼快</blockquote><br />\n我做緊3D 動畫，product promotion 果類，即係一條片由3d建模，到動畫，到rendering, 到後期特效都自己一個做哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係大陸同台灣都好多人研究緊呢類software，點解香港好似見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7c2489862f71561d13bd7391288cb338a6b00f","tid":466054,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:06:20.000Z","msg":"廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fd10a9d36ffb364952c406621c5802be9c2cd9","tid":466054,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"jobsdb應該幫到你 其實識build model應該幾搶手只係人工符唔符合你<br />\n<br />\n你知香港好多契弟都想你咩都識做曬但係又要underpaid <br />\n到時候工作量同人工成唔成正比 就要睇下你個老闆同公司係咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afe30daec0ebcf680bfb343d05b1b7e4f4c44b3","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>jobsdb應該幫到你 其實識build model應該幾搶手只係人工符唔符合你<br />\n<br />\n你知香港好多契弟都想你咩都識做曬但係又要underpaid <br />\n到時候工作量同人工成唔成正比 就要睇下你個老闆同公司係咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我間中都會碌jobsdb黎睇，但係同3D 有關既制作真係小得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工問題唔大，反正我有freelance 單接黎做"},{"pid":"fc7ea6450bdf52b2eb4f88aa40b552bdd5738ea6","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"