ww.cgvisual.com/forum/viewforum.php?f=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cgvisual.com%2Fforum%2Fviewforum.php%3Ff%3D11&d=9rRABI4mxnU312pk21FbRP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=cb0bfc7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cgvisual.com/forum/viewforum.php?f=11</a> 望一望</blockquote><br />\n巴打讀咩？"},{"pid":"3bb9ba66a51a063384c89004e6529b27630525c5","tid":466054,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>solidworks+keyshot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKeyshot係我讀書個陣product design個part我就黎手掟入去rend D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  簡單介面"},{"pid":"928b40ca367a7de646d3e3b2adc10c537ef67bba","tid":466054,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>OC配C4D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過oc好貴<br />\nUnity好少拎黎畫3D，多數maya max或者blender畫完再import入去整game用<br />\n<br />\n樣樣識啲但無樣精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋個人又懶，目前轉左行<br />\n自學緊unity，勤力返可以會入返行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都係做3D? 可唔可以分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncinema 4d+oc 真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\noc 唔係好貴，但要買display card 去玩oc就好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nunity 我冇研究過，好唔好用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學樓上咁講，真係要識埋programming<br />\n不過有分modelling 同 script 兩part啦<br />\nModelling個班識少少咪夠囉，大概知發生緊咩事<br />\n寫script個班唔通叫人畫圖畫公仔咩<br />\n我咩都係識少少架咋<br />\n做呢行工時又長人工又少<br />\n收得工黎食個飯就無哂時間要瞓覺<br />\n唉 當興趣玩下就算<br />\n<br />\nUnity識得畫下3D既，同識得dl人地open source 既script都可以拎黎寫下簡單game"},{"pid":"9606dc3ccd1d20ccdaccff9c63dadfcb3eb44d40","tid":466054,"uid":59472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"開緊工路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe6e05dfd2f5f9e0dd390c3d78aee1858d98b5a","tid":466054,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"houdini有無咩方法可以學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好多tutorial都預你識哂入面既野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a08278bced144d087c6bb56bb64c660c00ac6ff","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>OC配C4D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過oc好貴<br />\nUnity好少拎黎畫3D，多數maya max或者blender畫完再import入去整game用<br />\n<br />\n樣樣識啲但無樣精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋個人又懶，目前轉左行<br />\n自學緊unity，勤力返可以會入返行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打之前都係做3D? 可唔可以分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncinema 4d+oc 真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\noc 唔係好貴，但要買display card 去玩oc就好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nunity 我冇研究過，好唔好用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學樓上咁講，真係要識埋programming<br />\n不過有分modelling 同 script 兩part啦<br />\nModelling個班識少少咪夠囉，大概知發生緊咩事<br />\n寫script個班唔通叫人畫圖畫公仔咩<br />\n我咩都係識少少架咋<br />\n做呢行工時又長人工又少<br />\n收得工黎食個飯就無哂時間要瞓覺<br />\n唉 當興趣玩下就算<br />\n<br />\nUnity識得畫下3D既，同識得dl人地open source 既script都可以拎黎寫下簡單game</blockquote><br />\n點解香港呢行人工咁小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我係大陸接單做都有兩三皮一個月，返黎香港可以做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3f3c70fc2673cb1584ce726b861b4c7433197f","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>houdini有無咩方法可以學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好多tutorial都預你識哂入面既野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有好多入門教學"},{"pid":"7d3b23ed9601689c56ccfa17c8b47d4228b07f0a","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開緊工路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打做咩？"},{"pid":"dcceedb9e5f16223649a43b431bf4a6546ea8f0a","tid":466054,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>houdini有無咩方法可以學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好多tutorial都預你識哂入面既野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有好多入門教學</blockquote><br />\n跪求好想學好佢<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede4b05123837baeca3baa2fb3ce7f5e630844dc","tid":466054,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>houdini有無咩方法可以學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好多tutorial都預你識哂入面既野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有好多入門教學</blockquote><br />\n跪求好想學好佢<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇telegram?